Class SearchController

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.SearchController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable

    public class SearchController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    This class is the controller of the order list search screen for manager: Search.fxml and for staff: StaffSearch.fxml Can search the orders based on table number, dates and times intervals and ordered food.
    Since:
    2016-12-16
    Version:
